{"tid":1405052,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Krystal隔3年重站舞台 粉絲見f(x)合體感動哽咽","createTime":"2019-08-04T07:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T15:39:17.000Z","uid":213300,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0f07462d7aa218c869f2e60ab6de26249601012f","tid":1405052,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:29:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/4843207-krystal%e9%9a%943%e5%b9%b4%e9%87%8d%e7%ab%99%e8%88%9e%e5%8f%b0-%e7%b2%89%e7%b5%b2%e8%a6%8bfx%e5%90%88%e9%ab%94%e6%84%9f%e5%8b%95%e5%93%bd%e5%92%bd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F4843207-krystal%25e9%259a%25943%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e9%2587%258d%25e7%25ab%2599%25e8%2588%259e%25e5%258f%25b0-%25e7%25b2%2589%25e7%25b5%25b2%25e8%25a6%258bfx%25e5%2590%2588%25e9%25ab%2594%25e6%2584%259f%25e5%258b%2595%25e5%2593%25bd%25e5%2592%25bd%2F&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUBwEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=b258dab2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/4843207-krystal%e9%9a%943%e5%b9%b4%e9%87%8d%e7%ab%99%e8%88%9e%e5%8f%b0-%e7%b2%89%e7%b5%b2%e8%a6%8bfx%e5%90%88%e9%ab%94%e6%84%9f%e5%8b%95%e5%93%bd%e5%92%bd/</a><br />\nSMTOWN一連3日在日本東京巨蛋舉行家族演唱會，最引發關注的，就是各組合的成員會否 全部在這次演唱會合體。而自2015年就再無發表任何新作品的f(x)，也在中國籍成員Vict oria的缺席下進行了首次三人合體演出，Krystal也是闊別舞台3年後再度登台演出。 SMTOWN早前公開「SMTOWN LIVE 2019 IN TOKYO」的海報時，粉絲已經因見到海報上印上f (x)四人照片而興奮，雖然官方其後宣佈隊長Victoria將缺席演唱會，但至少許久沒有以 歌手身份活動的Krystal將重新站上舞台，讓人期待。 等到f(x)合體的來臨，Krystal也久違地以組合的Center登場，一連帶來了《Electric Sh ock》、《LA chA TA》、《4 Walls》、《Hot Summer》等歌曲，令現場不少粉絲感動哽 咽。 近年轉到演戲和時尚界發展的Krystal雖然已經3年沒有站上舞台，但仍擋不了在舞台上的 耀眼。大家看到f(x)合體畫面後紛紛留言：「等了這個舞台很久了」、「我都哭了，這是 真的嗎？」、「是想念的Krystal啊」、「歡迎回來啊Krystal」等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GelORKLkC3o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGelORKLkC3o&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUBwEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=5a12a9b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GelORKLkC3o</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝雪莉條仆街快撚d收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ea8e3b4bd4f1d28b8bcf02fa9be73559641a72","tid":1405052,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:57:42.000Z","msg":"宋茜黎唔到仲叫fx咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44ee35f4f26705b69c1ad36033eda3a122cb92e","tid":1405052,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06ea8e3b4bd4f1d28b8bcf02fa9be73559641a72","tid":1405052,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:57:42.000Z","msg":"宋茜黎唔到仲叫fx咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"f(x)唯四<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c41141eb349ac23d1660e827f51351d5846ce88","tid":1405052,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e44ee35f4f26705b69c1ad36033eda3a122cb92e","tid":1405052,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06ea8e3b4bd4f1d28b8bcf02fa9be73559641a72","tid":1405052,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:57:42.000Z","msg":"宋茜黎唔到仲叫fx咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"f(x)唯四<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-0